<plot>A young boy, Malachi, was captured as an infant and now is forced to work in a futuristic labyrinth of pipes. The only thing sustaining him is an old, faded postcard of a beach he once visited with his parents. But hope of escape presents itself when a young girl, Kael, forges an alliance and reveals that she knows a secret buried somewhere in the maze.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?433634</url></doc>
